<br>
Apollo wandered into the center of the villa looking around for Hestia. He made his way to the throne room, his eyes bouncing upon each thrown. Hestia was no where to be found.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do not make this difficult for me.&quot; he muttered under his breath. As he walked through the throne room he ran into the Graces(Charites) and Muses, squeeling and shrieking, arguing about something.<br>
<br>
&quot;Now why are we arguing so early in the morning?&quot; Apollo smiled, giving each a hug and a kiss on the cheek.<br>
<br>
&quot;Apollo, its nothing. Do not worry yourself over it. I am sure that you have much grander things on your mind.&quot; Calliope smiled.<br>
<br>
'In this you are right.' Apollo thought, but on the outside he just smiled and nodded as he was off to look for his aunt. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uo0ohestiao0o.showPublicProfile?language=EN>o0o hestia o0o</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/28/01 10:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=91.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Now lets get to the bottom of this...</span><hr size=1> ~after many hours have past she continued to stare up at the ceiling her hair way layed out onto the pillows as she gazed into nothing..her house laid in silence as well as she let out a small yawn~<br>
